        </div>

        <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
            <img src="https://store.storeimages.cdn-apple.com/8756/as-images.apple.com/is/44-alum-blue-sport-deepnavy-6s-nc?wid=2000&hei=2000&fmt=jpeg&qlt=95&.v=1599811389000" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body text-center">
                <h5 class="card-title">Apple Watch Series 6</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    อนาคตของสุขภาพ
